## Context7 — Mandatory Documentation Protocol

Use Context7 MCP for all library and tool documentation lookups in this project.

Workflow (always in this order):
1. resolve-library-id → pass the library name, get the Context7 ID
2. query-docs → pass the ID + specific query, get current docs
3. Implement from those docs — never from training data

Priority IDs for this project:
- Hermes Agent: /nousresearch/hermes-agent

Use for: Hermes config schema, skill file format, gateway config, 
MCP server registration, memory file structure, tool invocation.
